{
  "DialogueName": "NewDialogue",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "nodeId": 0,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "你来了，那符……",
      "nextNodeIndex": 1,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 1,
      "actorId": 0,
      "dialogueText": "换掉了。",
      "nextNodeIndex": 2,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 2,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "你不是一般人。",
      "nextNodeIndex": 3,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 3,
      "actorId": 0,
      "dialogueText": "。。。",
      "nextNodeIndex": 4,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 4,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "我起初以为你只是阴气重，能看见我，可现在我知道了",
      "nextNodeIndex": 5,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 5,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "吹过你的风，有苦水的味道。",
      "nextNodeIndex": 6,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 6,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "眼前这条河，叫苦水。人们说是众生眼泪汇聚的。",
      "nextNodeIndex": 7,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 7,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "你在那边，见惯了死别。有流过眼泪吗？",
      "nextNodeIndex": 8,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 8,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "你来，其实是带我走的吗？",
      "nextNodeIndex": 9,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 9,
      "actorId": 0,
      "dialogueText": "老实说，我还没有这个想法。",
      "nextNodeIndex": 10,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 10,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "我不要，我不能走。",
      "nextNodeIndex": 11,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 11,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "庙里的人，他们还会饿的。冬天快到了，逃荒的人会越来越多。我不能再让他们挨饿了。",
      "nextNodeIndex": 12,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 12,
      "actorId": 0,
      "dialogueText": "",
      "nextNodeIndex": -1,
      "isChoiceNode": true,
      "animationTrigger": "",
      "choices": [
        {
          "choiceText": "告诉她久留人间的危害",
          "targetNodeIndex": 13,
          "conditions": []
        },
        {
          "choiceText": "什么都不说",
          "targetNodeIndex": 15,
          "conditions": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 13,
      "actorId": 0,
      "dialogueText": "鬼也是会死的。我想朱圆不会放过你的",
      "nextNodeIndex": 14,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 14,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "我知道",
      "nextNodeIndex": 15,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 15,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "吴门老家的莲花，都是六月里开。我娘说，我生在三月，桃花都谢了，杏花也谢了，就剩几棵晚梅，还零零星星地挂着。",
      "nextNodeIndex": 16,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 16,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "可我做错了吗？为什么是我呢？",
      "nextNodeIndex": 17,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 17,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "为什么是他们呢？",
      "nextNodeIndex": 18,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 18,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "为什么这个世道，要把人变成这样？",
      "nextNodeIndex": 19,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 19,
      "actorId": 0,
      "dialogueText": "阿慈，你冷静点。",
      "nextNodeIndex": 20,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 20,
      "actorId": 0,
      "dialogueText": "（就在这时候——包里的那符纸自己飞了出来。）！",
      "nextNodeIndex": 21,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 21,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "（伸出手，双指一夹，把那符纸夹在指间。）",
      "nextNodeIndex": 22,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 22,
      "actorId": 0,
      "dialogueText": "……不是你想的那样。",
      "nextNodeIndex": 23,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 23,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "我知道。你是好人",
      "nextNodeIndex": 24,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 24,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "好人也会做坏事的。我嫁过去之前，我娘也是这么说的。",
      "nextNodeIndex": 25,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 25,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "你走吧。",
      "nextNodeIndex": 26,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 26,
      "actorId": 0,
      "dialogueText": "阿慈——",
      "nextNodeIndex": 27,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 27,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "我见过你们这种人。你们总是有道理的。你们总是对的。你们说，人死了就该走，该去投胎，该喝了那碗汤，把什么都忘了。",
      "nextNodeIndex": 28,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 28,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "可我不想忘。",
      "nextNodeIndex": 29,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 29,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "我不想忘了吴门的莲花，不想忘了我娘，不想忘了那些饿着肚子走在这条路上的人。我不想忘了那一刀有多痛，不想忘了为什么会有那一刀。我不想忘了人是怎么变成鬼的",
      "nextNodeIndex": 30,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 30,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "然后你们说，这样不好。这样不对。这样会变成厉鬼，会害人，会被天收。",
      "nextNodeIndex": 31,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 31,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "我害过谁？我做错了吗？",
      "nextNodeIndex": 32,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 32,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "你说，我这样的人，该不该被超度？",
      "nextNodeIndex": 34,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
    {
      "nodeId": 33,
      "actorId": 6,
      "dialogueText": "那就不用你动手了。",
      "nextNodeIndex": -1,
      "isChoiceNode": false,
      "animationTrigger": ""
    },
